,Recommended,233150,10742555,"Posted: 23 June, 2014",all,General Fuddy Duddy Sr.,"Takes me back to the good old days. Wait, I'm Russian."
,Recommended,233150,17563342,"Posted: 16 August, 2015",all,jsabsd,"Seldom have I ever been so impressed with a game as this. It's just simple, fast, and fun. I am actully gifting copies to many of my friends.If you want something that scales to be a challenge and rises with your skill level, this is it. It will inevitably best you, but the fun is seeing how long you can avoid it.I have two actual gripes:The first gripe is that the firing/boosting ""non-stop"" missions don't always appear to count correctly. For example, you continuous fire 20 chain-kills to reach MAX combo but the mission shows that you've only been credited for 3 kills. This really sucks on the one for a 30 chain.The other gripe is that the entire range of ""at MAX combo"" missions rely on more serendipity than actual skill. There will often be gaps in the spawn rate long enough for the combo counter to drop the bonus. Only then does the target spawn, and with nothing around to build back the combo counter."
