,Recommended,233150,22302061,"Posted: 8 April, 2016",all,Snuggles,"It's utterly insane and I'm terrible at it - but it's good old fashioned fun. Some caveats you may not pick up on from watching videos - The menus are ♥♥♥♥in awful, especially if you want to configure a controller. Also the color scheme can wear on the eyes after a few minutes for me. Honestly though, if you watch a video of the gameplay and it looks like reckless nutty fun to you - it is probably worth the buy.Oh and obviously don't come here looking for a complex narrative or anything like that, this is a straight to the point old school arcade shooter."
