76561198091682568,Recommended,233150,9945678,"Posted: 26 April, 2014",all,DetectiveLizard,"LUFTRAUSERS is an interesting bullet hell game based on the flash game LUFTRAUSER. Your goal is to survive long enough to get a new high score by taking down enemies and thats about it. You dogfight with planes which you can get upgrades that work in different ways. The best part in my opinion is the music as it is one of the few games that make me feel stress and excitement when dealing with mass numbers of enemies, plus each plane upgrade changes the music giving you multiple tracks to listen to. The retro style graphics are a good call to use as simplicity makes the best of this game.8.5/10 A simple but well made arcade game that will in the long run have a lasting appeal to any Steam user. Great music, fun gameplay and the perfect game to play in short bursts."
